front.title: •Commander Brandei (V)
front.gametext: Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots (3 if Judicator). Your total battle destiny here is +1 for each TIE subtype here or aboard same starship. During your turn, may take into hand one launch bay or non-unique TIE from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.
front.lore: Technical Services Officer of the Fleet Support Branch. Responsible for keeping Executor's 12 TIE squadrons serviced and combat ready. Just received transfer to Judicator.
